item.description:
@Unhandled wrote:

Tape looks like shit, the drop shadow at the bottom removes all possibility of it having depth, and the yellow part’s drop shadow sticks out on the sides. I would also move the wavy thing and the text so the wave goes through the middle of the text. Parts of the text look anti aliased and some parts don’t (probably not your fault), and the text should have a drop shadow imo.
